STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Stanley A. BETTERS, Jr., Defendant-Petitioner. C-976 September Term 2018
082718 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000239-18 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
